INSERT INTO limits__guild_limits (
                guild_id,
                limit_name,
                limit_type,
                stings,
                limit_per,
                limit_time
            )
            VALUES (
                $1, 
                $2, 
                $3, 
                $4, 
                $5,
                make_interval(secs => $6)
            )
            RETURNING limit_id
